Public Routes
User Registration
POST /api/users/register
User Login
POST /api/users/login
Forgot Password
POST /api/users/forgot-password
Reset Password
POST /api/users/reset-password

Retrieve Blog Posts
GET /api/blogs
Query Parameters:
page (optional): Page number for pagination.
perPage (optional): Number of posts per page.
Search Blog Posts
GET /api/blogs/search
Query Parameters:
title (optional): Search by blog post title.
author (optional): Search by blog post author name.
Filter Blog Posts
GET /api/blogs/filter
Query Parameters:
tags (optional): Comma-separated list of tags.
date (optional): Filter by date (e.g., "2024-08-15").
Generate Blog Content Suggestions
POST /api/ai/content-suggestions
Request Body:
json
Copy code
{
"keywords": ["string"],
"topic": "string"
}

User Routes
User Logout
POST /api/users/logout
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Update User Profile
PUT /api/users/profile
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Refresh Token
POST /api/users/refresh-token
Request Body:
json
Copy code
{
"refreshToken": "string"
}

Create Blog Post
POST /api/blogs
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Update Blog Post
PUT /api/blogs/{blogId}
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Delete Blog Post
DELETE /api/blogs/{blogId}
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

Admin Routes
Admin Create Blog Post
POST /api/admin/blogs
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Admin Update Blog Post
PUT /api/admin/blogs/{blogId}
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Admin Delete Blog Post
DELETE /api/admin/blogs/{blogId}
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Admin Get All Users
GET /api/admin/users
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Admin Update User Role
PUT /api/admin/users/{userId}/role
Request Body:
json
Copy code
{
"role": "string" (e.g., "Admin", "User")
}

Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Admin Delete User
DELETE /api/admin/users/{userId}
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
AI Routes
Generate Blog Content Suggestions
POST /api/ai/content-suggestions
Request Body:
json
Copy code
{
"keywords": ["string"],
"topic": "string"
}
